# GCP staging — committed static config (single source of truth)
# Dynamic values (Cloud Run URL, bucket names, CDN IP) come from Pulumi outputs.
# This file is intentionally NOT gitignored so CI can read it reliably.

# staging は独自ドメイン・CDN (Cloud CDN) を使用しない
# GCS 静的ウェブサイトホスティングを直接使用
CLOUD_CUSTOM_DOMAIN=""
# Firebase config is stored in GitHub Secrets (FIREBASE_API_KEY etc.) — not here
